</nav></header><main aria-label="main content"><div class="speakable">
      <b data-is-speakable>Amitav Ghosh's 'Gun Island' Is Fiction In The Face Of Climate Change</b>   <b data-is-speakable>Ghosh's latest book, <em>Gun Island,</em> is a modern retelling of a Bengali myth. He believes old legends have a lot to teach us about how to think about the catastrophic effects of climate change.</b>
